{"type":"message","id":"3a84b0d1","parentId":"7b6dabc9","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:38:53.900Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_b5ugw1dn8g2w_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"总计 12\ndrwxrwxr-x 2 halei halei 4096  5月  4 08:59 .\ndrwxrwxr-x 3 halei halei 4096  5月  4 08:59 ..\n-rwxrwxr-x 1 halei halei 2434  5月  4 08:59 search.py\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nsearxng_search.py — Search via SearXNG instance\nUsage:\n  python3 search.py \"query\" [--host HOST] [--engines ENGINES] [--lang LANG] [--time-range TIME_RANGE] [--limit LIMIT]\n  HOST defaults to http://localhost:8888\n\"\"\"\nimport json\nimport sys\nimport urllib.request\nimport urllib.parse\nimport argparse\n\n\ndef search(query, host=\"http://192.168.31.146:8888\", engines=None, categories=None,\n           lang=None, time_range=None, limit=10):\n    params = {\n        \"q\": query,\n        \"format\": \"json\",\n        \"pageno\": 1,\n    }\n    if engines:\n        params[\"engines\"] = engines\n    if categories:\n        params[\"categories\"] = categories\n    if lang:\n        params[\"language\"] = lang\n    if time_range:\n        params[\"time_range\"] = time_range"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":143,"aggregated":"总计 12\ndrwxrwxr-x 2 halei halei 4096  5月  4 08:59 .\ndrwxrwxr-x 3 halei halei 4096  5月  4 08:59 ..\n-rwxrwxr-x 1 halei halei 2434  5月  4 08:59 search.py\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nsearxng_search.py — Search via SearXNG instance\nUsage:\n  python3 search.py \"query\" [--host HOST] [--engines ENGINES] [--lang LANG] [--time-range TIME_RANGE] [--limit LIMIT]\n  HOST defaults to http://localhost:8888\n\"\"\"\nimport json\nimport sys\nimport urllib.request\nimport urllib.parse\nimport argparse\n\n\ndef search(query, host=\"http://192.168.31.146:8888\", engines=None, categories=None,\n           lang=None, time_range=None, limit=10):\n    params = {\n        \"q\": query,\n        \"format\": \"json\",\n        \"pageno\": 1,\n    }\n    if engines:\n        params[\"engines\"] = engines\n    if categories:\n        params[\"categories\"] = categories\n    if lang:\n        params[\"language\"] = lang\n    if time_range:\n        params[\"time_range\"] = time_range","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780922333898}}
{"type":"message","id":"d0c8545d","parentId":"3a84b0d1","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:39:07.110Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"SearXNG 当前**不能用**，原因和现状：\n\n**🔴 现状**\n- Skill 是装好的（`searxng-search/scripts/search.py`）\n- 默认地址 `http://192.168.31.146:8888` 是你内网（家里 NAS / 局域网），从这台 Surface 走不通，跑了 `python3 search.py \"test\"` 返回空 `[]`\n- 外部 workers.dev 那个域名也连不上（你之前可能备过一个公网反代，现在挂了）\n\n**🟢 能立刻用的备选**\n- `web_search`（内置多引擎：Tavily / Brave / Perplexity）—— 想要我直接搜什么就告诉我\n- `tavily-search` skill —— 适合深度搜索，质量比 SearXNG 高\n- `multi-search-engine` skill —— 聚合多源\n\n**🛠️ 修 SearXNG 的几种思路**\n1. 看看 `192.168.31.146:8888` 那个实例还活着没（你内网能不能访问 `http://192.168.31.146:8888`？）\n2. 在这台机器本地用 Docker 起一个：`docker run -d -p 8888:8888 --name searxng searxng/searxng`，把默认 host 改成 `localhost:8888`\n3. 如果你需要我从外网也能调，得有个公网入口（CF Tunnel / 反代）\n\n要我用 `web_search` 先顶着，还是你想先排查内网那个实例？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":320,"output":325,"cacheRead":53676,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54321,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780922333911,"responseId":"0675eadebd3fb94ea9e3358784e81a39"}}
