{"type":"message","id":"32120dba","parentId":"5cdc1a0e","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:40:31.722Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到了。SearXNG 服务是通的（HTTP 200，页面 2026.5.15 版本），但**所有 6 个配置的搜索引擎全挂**：\n\n| 引擎 | 状态 |\n|---|---|\n| brave | timeout |\n| duckduckgo | timeout |\n| google | timeout |\n| karmasearch | access denied |\n| startpage | timeout |\n| wikipedia | timeout |\n\n连接超时 + 一个 access denied，说明不是网络问题（你浏览器能开页面，但页面里调引擎超时）。这台机器大概率出口被限制 / 被搜索引擎识别为机房 IP 屏蔽了。三个方向验证一下："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sremb7pe168s_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"--- DDG ---\"; curl -sS -m 6 -o /dev/null -w \"HTTP %{http_code} | DNS %{time_namelookup}s | connect %{time_connect}s | total %{time_total}s\\n\" \"https://html.duckduckgo.com/html/?q=test\" 2>&1\necho \"--- Google ---\"; curl -sS -m 6 -o /dev/null -w \"HTTP %{http_code} | DNS %{time_namelookup}s | connect %{time_connect}s | total %{time_total}s\\n\" \"https://www.google.com/search?q=test\" 2>&1\necho \"--- Brave ---\"; curl -sS -m 6 -o /dev/null -w \"HTTP %{http_code} | DNS %{time_namelookup}s | connect %{time_connect}s | total %{time_total}s\\n\" \"https://search.brave.com/search?q=test\" 2>&1\necho \"--- Wikipedia ---\"; curl -sS -m 6 -o /dev/null -w \"HTTP %{http_code} | DNS %{time_namelookup}s | connect %{time_connect}s | total %{time_total}s\\n\" \"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Test\" 2>&1\necho \"--- DNS ---\"; cat /etc/resolv.conf 2>&1 | head -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":265,"output":437,"cacheRead":54343,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55045,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780922423670,"responseId":"0675eb3866ff8aa4218f1ed9df054d13"}}
