{"type":"message","id":"351ea846","parentId":"3a0feabd","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:47:26.540Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"两个都连不上 Docker Hub 的 registry（不是搜索引擎的问题，是这台机器 dockerd 出口到 registry-1.docker.io 也超时）。这跟之前 `hub.docker.com` 443 超时、搜索引擎 timeout 都是**同一类问题**：这台机器的 HTTPS 出站被网络层限制。让我看看有没有镜像加速器配置："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2relnv5yut6k_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"--- /etc/docker/daemon.json ---\"\ncat /etc/docker/daemon.json 2>&1\necho\necho \"--- check if mirror reachable ---\"\nfor m in docker.m.daocloud.io dockerproxy.com mirror.baidubce.com docker.mirrors.ustc.edu.cn registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com; do\n  printf \"%-45s \" \"$m\"\n  curl -sS -m 4 -o /dev/null -w \"HTTP %{http_code} | %{time_total}s\\n\" \"https://$m/v2/\" 2>&1\ndone\necho\necho \"--- test if registry-1.docker.io reaches via DNS ---\"\ngetent hosts registry-1.docker.io 2>&1\nnslookup registry-1.docker.io 2>&1 | tail -5\necho\necho \"--- direct curl to registry ---\"\ncurl -sS -m 8 -o /dev/null -w \"HTTP %{http_code} | DNS %{time_namelookup}s | connect %{time_connect}s | total %{time_total}s\\n\" \"https://registry-1.docker.io/v2/\" 2>&1","timeout":90}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":115,"output":349,"cacheRead":59742,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60206,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780922836846,"responseId":"0675ecd525943af935b5fdd263c3cf95"}}
{"type":"message","id":"312d4cc6","parentId":"351ea846","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:47:34.138Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2relnv5yut6k_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"--- /etc/docker/daemon.json ---\n{\n  \"registry-mirrors\": [\n    \"https://dockerpull.com\",\n    \"https://dhub.kubesre.xyz\",\n    \"https://hub.rat.dev\",\n    \"https://docker.nju.edu.cn\",\n    \"https://registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com\",\n    \"https://registry.docker-cn.com\"\n  ]\n}\n\n--- check if mirror reachable ---\ndocker.m.daocloud.io                          HTTP 401 | 0.188492s\ndockerproxy.com                               curl: (28) Failed to connect to dockerproxy.com port 443 after 2209 ms: 连接超时\nHTTP 000 | 2.210051s\nmirror.baidubce.com                           curl: (6) Could not resolve host: mirror.baidubce.com\nHTTP 000 | 0.024483s\ndocker.mirrors.ustc.edu.cn                    curl: (6) Could not resolve host: docker.mirrors.ustc.edu.cn\nHTTP 000 | 0.026763s\nregistry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com             HTTP 401 | 0.238229s\n\n--- test if registry-1.docker.io reaches via DNS ---\n2a03:2880:f127:83:face:b00c:0:25de registry-1.docker.io\nName:\tregistry-1.docker.io\nAddress: 168.143.171.189\nName:\tregistry-1.docker.io\nAddress: 2a03:2880:f127:83:face:b00c:0:25de\n\n\n--- direct curl to registry ---\ncurl: (28) Failed to connect to registry-1.docker.io port 443 after 4202 ms: 连接超时\nHTTP 000 | DNS 0.000889s | connect 0.000000s | total 4.202343s\n\n(Command exited with code 28)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":28,"durationMs":7123,"aggregated":"--- /etc/docker/daemon.json ---\n{\n  \"registry-mirrors\": [\n    \"https://dockerpull.com\",\n    \"https://dhub.kubesre.xyz\",\n    \"https://hub.rat.dev\",\n    \"https://docker.nju.edu.cn\",\n    \"https://registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com\",\n    \"https://registry.docker-cn.com\"\n  ]\n}\n\n--- check if mirror reachable ---\ndocker.m.daocloud.io                