{"type":"message","id":"2dca0e95","parentId":"312d4cc6","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:47:44.658Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"有戏：\n\n- `daemon.json` 配了 6 个镜像加速器\n- `docker.m.daocloud.io` 和 `registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com` **通的**（HTTP 401 = 端点存在需要认证，正常）\n- 其它几个解析失败/超时\n- 直连 `registry-1.docker.io` 解析到的是 Cloudflare 的 IPv6，被卡\n\n`docker pull` 没用上镜像源（依然走 `registry-1.docker.io` 超时），说明 dockerd 没在用 mirror 配置 —— 可能 mirror 列表里大多挂了，dockerd fallback 回主站。手动指定能通的镜像源再拉："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4j0yub19w5ri_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"--- Test mirror API endpoints (pull requires /v2/) ---\"\nfor m in docker.m.daocloud.io registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com; do\n  echo \"=== $m ===\"\n  curl -sS -m 6 -o /dev/null -w \"  /v2/  : HTTP %{http_code} | %{time_total}s\\n\" \"https://$m/v2/\" 2>&1\n  curl -sS -m 6 -o /dev/null -w \"  /v2/searxng/... : HTTP %{http_code} | %{time_total}s\\n\" \"https://$m/v2/searxng/searxng/manifests/latest\" 2>&1\ndone","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":435,"output":341,"cacheRead":60192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60968,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780922854152,"responseId":"0675ece695ca0fb7877769bd885535db"}}
