{"type":"message","id":"2346e47e","parentId":"afc1ec47","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:47:51.625Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"两个镜像源都活着，API 端点能调到。401 是 docker registry 标准的\"无认证\"响应，说明 v2 协议 OK。但 dockerd 没自动用这些 mirror 拉 —— 应该是 mirror 列表里挂掉的把\"列表健康度\"拉低了，dockerd 直接 skip。我直接**改 daemon.json**只用活的源，然后重启 dockerd："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4c13hh9yodk9_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /etc/docker/daemon.json 2>&1; echo \"---\"; ls -la /etc/docker/ 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":145,"output":129,"cacheRead":60954,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61228,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780922866248,"responseId":"0675ecf293364bddf6e7ad0d98822e41"}}
