{"type":"message","id":"7621d749","parentId":"e8fd4c4c","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:52:08.164Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"用户说 web 页面默认的 Bing 搜索可以用。结合之前我查到的：\n- SearXNG 所有海外引擎 timeout\n- Docker Hub registry-1.docker.io 直连超时\n- 配的 6 个镜像源大多挂掉，只有 `docker.m.daocloud.io` 和 `registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com` 活的\n- dockerd 没自动用 mirror（可能列表里挂的太多）\n\n用户现在告诉我 **Bing 在 web 页面上能用**——意思是他浏览器里能直连 Bing。我需要：\n\n1. 把 SearXNG 的搜索引擎从海外换成能用的（Bing）+ SearXNG 自带的 wikipedia 等本地类\n2. 修 docker mirror 让 pull 能用\n\n先看 SearXNG 的 settings.yml 在哪："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i4xy1v1ycawt_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"--- SearXNG mount ---\"\ndocker inspect searxng --format='{{range .Mounts}}{{.Source}} -> {{.Destination}}{{\"\\n\"}}{{end}}' 2>&1\necho\necho \"--- host /srv /opt 查 searxng 目录 ---\"\nls -la /home/halei/searxng 2>/dev/null || true\nls -la ~/searxng 2>/dev/null || true\nls -la /opt/searxng 2>/dev/null || true\nsudo find / -maxdepth 5 -name \"settings.yml\" -path \"*searxng*\" 2>/dev/null | head -5","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":60501,"output":345,"cacheRead":1266,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62112,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780923118835,"responseId":"0675edefe955b1fcfcc890bf0b3abfe1"}}
