{"type":"message","id":"e5e1de2b","parentId":"6ea9f481","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:52:53.966Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"SearXNG 现在的 enabled general 引擎里没有 bing 也没有 google（都 disabled）。我得**编辑 settings.yml 把 bing 启用、google/duckduckgo/brave/startpage/wikipedia 留着但加代理或测试哪些能直连**。\n\n但等等——用户说\"Bing 在 web 页面上能用\"，**这不等于** SearXNG 容器内能用。SearXNG 容器抓 Bing 时走的是容器自己的网络。我先**直接测容器内能不能通 Bing**："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ev44rumqk56y_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"--- Test connectivity from inside SearXNG container ---\"\ndocker exec searxng sh -c '\n  for url in \"https://www.bing.com\" \"https://cn.bing.com\" \"https://www.baidu.com\" \"https://www.sogou.com\" \"https://en.wikipedia.org\"; do\n    printf \"%-35s \" \"$url\"\n    curl -sS -m 5 -o /dev/null -w \"HTTP %{http_code} | %{time_total}s\\n\" \"$url\" 2>&1\n  done\n  echo \"---\"\n  echo \"container DNS:\"\n  cat /etc/resolv.conf 2>&1 | head -3\n'","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":177,"output":286,"cacheRead":64944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65407,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780923163253,"responseId":"0675ee1b6d94587045238db4eb82f02b"}}
