{"type":"message","id":"5bed63e5","parentId":"ed27d225","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:53:41.606Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**关键发现**：\n\n- 容器内**能通 Bing**（8.57s 慢但能通，`cn.bing.com` 0.74s 超快）\n- **能通 Baidu** (5.36s)、**Sogou** (1.74s)\n- Wikipedia/DDG 海外站：Network is unreachable（IPv6 路由问题，容器走的是 Docker 默认网桥 + Google DNS 8.8.8.8）\n\n容器本身能从公网到 Bing/Baidu/Sogou！**所以 SearXNG 不是网络问题，是 engines 配置问题**。我之前用脚本里默认 192.168.31.146 走不通是因为——等等，那个 192.168.31.146 实际是 SearXNG 容器映射的端口。让我重新看 skill 脚本调的是哪个 host："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0fuce5hmgg2i_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/searxng-search/scripts/search.py 2>&1 | head -20\necho \"===\"\n# 容器响应了但 timeout/empty。问题是 engines 都没启用\n# 让我从容器内直接 query SearXNG API 看哪个引擎在工作\ndocker exec searxng sh -c 'wget -qO- --timeout=20 \"http://localhost:8080/search?q=test&format=json\" 2>&1' | head -c 2000","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":289,"output":325,"cacheRead":65984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66598,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780923213185,"responseId":"0675ee4dbd29d6c78f4faa1a523d9615"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a865b496","parentId":"5bed63e5","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:53:45.535Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0fuce5hmgg2i_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nsearxng_search.py — Search via SearXNG instance\nUsage:\n  python3 search.py \"query\" [--host HOST] [--engines ENGINES] [--lang LANG] [--time-range TIME_RANGE] [--limit LIMIT]\n  HOST defaults to http://localhost:8888\n\"\"\"\nimport json\nimport sys\nimport urllib.request\nimport urllib.parse\nimport argparse\n\n\ndef search(query, host=\"http://192.168.31.146:8888\", engines=None, categories=None,\n           lang=None, time_range=None, limit=10):\n    params = {\n        \"q\": query,\n        \"format\": \"json\",\n        \"pageno\": 1,\n===\n{\"query\": \"test\", \"number_of_results\": 0, \"results\": [], \"answers\": [], \"corrections\": [], \"infoboxes\": [], \"suggestions\": [], \"unresponsive_engines\": [[\"brave\", \"timeout\"], [\"duckduckgo\", \"timeout\"], [\"google\", \"timeout\"], [\"karmasearch\", \"timeout\"], [\"startpage\", \"timeout\"], [\"wikipedia\", \"timeout\"]]}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3239,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nsearxng_search.py — Search via SearXNG instance\nUsage:\n  python3 search.py \"query\" [--host HOST] [--engines ENGINES] [--lang LANG] [--time-range TIME_RANGE] [--limit LIMIT]\n  HOST defaults to http://localhost:8888\n\"\"\"\nimport json\nimport sys\nimport urllib.request\nimport urllib.parse\nimport argparse\n\n\ndef search(query, host=\"http://192.168.31.146:8888\", engines=None, categories=None,\n           lang=None, time_range=None, limit=10):\n    params = {\n        \"q\": query,\n        \"format\": \"json\",\n        \"pageno\": 1,\n===\n{\"query\": \"test\", \"number_of_results\": 0, \"results\": [], \"answers\": [], \"corrections\": [], \"infoboxes\": [], \"suggestions\": [], \"unresponsive_engines\": [[\"brave\", \"timeout\"], [\"duckduckgo\", \"timeout\"], [\"google\", \"timeout\"], [\"karmasearch\", \"timeout\"], [\"startpage\", \"timeout\"], [\"wikipedia\", \"timeout\"]]}","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780923225532}}
{"type":"message","id":"32f19558","parentId":"a865b496","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:53:54.378Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**找到根因了**：SearXNG 的 `unresponsive_engines` 列表是 brave/duckduckgo/google/karmasearch/startpage/wikipedia —— **没有 baidu, sogou, bing**！说明这些是**被显式禁用**的。\n\n但等等，bing 是 `disabled: true`，而 baidu/sogou 之前显示 ON —— 让我再看一遍到底哪些 engine 在配置里 disabled，哪些 enabled。问题的关键：**SearXNG 的当前 enabled engines 应该返回结果，但返回 0 个**——这只能说明 enabled engines 的请求路径走不通。\n\n更可能的解释：**SearXNG 用的 `default` engines 是 user override，settings.yml 里**没有** `default` 段。让我搜下 `engines:` 第二处出现："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9iv7bietabzv_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"^engines:\" /home/halei/searxng-data/settings.yml 2>&1\necho \"===\"\n# SearXNG 有两处 engines 段：第一个是 engines 段（详细配置），第二个是 use_default_settings 之类的\n# 实际生效看 yml 顶层\nsed -n '1,50p' /home/halei/searxng-data/settings.yml 2>&1 | head -50"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":268,"output":285,"cacheRead":66584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67137,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780923225553,"responseId":"0675ee5a12022fbb4032603db057ba00"}}
{"type":"message","id":"dc7a115e","parentId":"32f19558","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:53:55.174Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9iv7bietabzv_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"302:engines:\n===\ngeneral:\n  # Debug mode, only for development. Is overwritten by ${SEARXNG_DEBUG}\n  debug: false\n  # displayed name\n  instance_name: \"SearXNG\"\n  # For example: https://example.com/privacy\n  privacypolicy_url: false\n  # use true to use your own donation page written in searx/info/en/donate.md\n  # use false to disable the donation link\n  donation_url: false\n  # mailto:contact@example.com\n  contact_url: false\n  # record stats\n  enable_metrics: true\n  # expose stats in open metrics format at /metrics\n  # leave empty to disable (no password set)\n  # open_metrics: <password>\n  open_metrics: ''\n\nbrand:\n  docs_url: https://docs.searxng.org/\n  public_instances: https://searx.space\n  wiki_url: https://github.com/searxng/searxng/wiki\n  issue_url: https://github.com/searxng/searxng/issues\n  # custom:\n  #   # Custom entries in the footer: [title]: [link]\n  #   links:\n  #     Uptime: https://uptime.searxng.org/history/darmarit-org\n  #     About: \"https://searxng.org\"\n  # pwa_colors:\n  #   # Custom settings for PWA icon an colors used in manifest.json\n  #   # Default colors are:\n  #    theme_color_light: \"#3050ff\"\n  #    background_color_light: \"fff\"\n  #    theme_color_dark: \"#58f\"\n  #    background_color_dark: \"#222428\"\n  #    theme_color_black: \"#3050ff\"\n  #    background_color_black: \"#000\"\n\nsearch:\n  # Filter results. 0: None, 1: Moderate, 2: Strict\n  safe_search: 0\n  # Existing autocomplete backends: \"360search\", \"baidu\", \"bing\", \"brave\", \"dbpedia\", \"duckduckgo\", \"google\",\n  # \"yandex\", \"mwmbl\", \"naver\", \"seznam\", \"sogou\", \"startpage\", \"swisscows\", \"quark\", \"qwant\", \"wikipedia\" -\n  # leave blank to turn it off by default.\n  autocomplete: \"\"\n  # minimun characters to type before autocompleter starts\n  autocomplete_min: 4\n  # backend for the favicon near URL in search results.\n  # Available resolvers: \"allesedv\", \"duckduckgo\", \"google\", \"yandex\" - leave blank to turn it off by default."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":119,"aggregated":"302:engines:\n===\ngeneral:\n  # Debug mode, only for development. Is overwritten by ${SEARXNG_DEBUG}\n  debug: false\n  # displayed name\n  instance_name: \"SearXNG\"\n  # For example: https://example.com/privacy\n  privacypolicy_url: false\n  # use true to use your own donation page written in searx/info/en/donate.md\n  # use false to disable the donation link\n  donation_url: false\n  # mailto:contact@example.com\n  contact_url: false\n  # record stats\n  enable_metrics: true\n  # expose stats in open metrics format at /metrics\n  # leave empty to disable (no password set)\n  # open_metrics: <password>\n  open_metrics: ''\n\nbrand:\n  docs_url: https://docs.searxng.org/\n  public_instances: https://searx.space\n  wiki_url: https://github.com/searxng/searxng/wiki\n  issue_url: https://github.com/searxng/searxng/issues\n  # custom:\n  #   # Custom entries in the footer: [title]: [link]\n  #   links:\n  #     Uptime: https://uptime.searxng.org/history/darmarit-org\n  #     About: \"https://searxng.org\"\n  # pwa_colors:\n  #   # Custom settings for PWA icon an colors used in manifest.json\n  #   # Default colors are:\n  #    theme_color_light: \"#3050ff\"\n  #    background_color_light: \"fff\"\n  #    theme_color_dark: \"#58f\"\n  #    background_color_dark: \"#222428\"\n  #    theme_color_black: \"#3050ff\"\n  #    background_color_black: \"#000\"\n\nsearch:\n  # Filter results. 0: None, 1: Moderate, 2: Strict\n  safe_search: 0\n  # Existing autocomplete backends: \"360search\", \"baidu\", \"bing\", \"brave\", \"dbpedia\", \"duckduckgo\", \"google\",\n  # \"yandex\", \"mwmbl\", \"naver\", \"seznam\", \"sogou\", \"startpage\", \"swisscows\", \"quark\", \"qwant\", \"wikipedia\" -\n  # leave blank to turn it off by default.\n  autocomplete: \"\"\n  # minimun characters to type before autocompleter starts\n  autocomplete_min: 4\n  # backend for the favicon near URL in search results.\n  # Available resolvers: \"allesedv\", \"duckduckgo\", \"google\", \"yandex\" - leave blank to turn it off by default.","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780923235169}}
{"type":"message","id":"ae930d8e","parentId":"dc7a115e","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:54:03.696Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OK 找到关键：**settings.yml 里没有 `use_default_settings: true` 也没有显式 `default` 字段**。`engines:` 段在 line 302 开始。\n\n**SearXNG 的逻辑**：\n- 如果 `use_default_settings: true` 或不设置 → 用内置默认 engines（`baidu, bing, duckduckgo, google, ...`）\n- 你的 `engines:` 段是显式列表，**覆盖**默认值。每个 engine 没 `disabled: true` 的会启用\n\n我之前没看仔细。让我用 python 解析出**实际启用**的引擎："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g12xmc4aac69_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'PY'\nimport yaml\nwith open('/home/halei/searxng-data/settings.yml') as f:\n    cfg = yaml.safe_load(f)\neng = cfg.get('engines', [])\nprint(f\"Total entries: {len(eng)}\")\non, off = [], []\nfor e in eng:\n    name = e.get('name', '?')\n    if e.get('disabled'):\n        off.append(name)\n    else:\n        on.append(name)\nprint(f\"\\nENABLED ({len(on)}):\")\nfor n in on: print(f\"  {n}\")\nprint(f\"\\nDISABLED ({len(off)}):\")\nfor n in off: print(f\"  {n}\")\nPY"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":610,"output":302,"cacheRead":67123,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68035,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780923235201,"responseId":"0675ee63765dbb075b583a6e7d949ec2"}}
