{"type":"message","id":"6a47ec01","parentId":"cfb905ba","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:54:16.261Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**谜底揭开**：\n\n- 启用的（114 个）几乎全是海外引擎：google, duckduckgo, brave, wikipedia, startpage, bing images, bing news, bing videos, **但 `bing`（general）被禁用了**\n- 国内的 `baidu, sogou, presearch, bilibili, 360search, quark, chinaso` 等全 disabled\n\n容器内**能通 cn.bing.com / baidu / sogou**，所以：\n- **启用 `bing`**（general 引擎）—— 你说浏览器能开 Bing，容器内 cn.bing.com 0.74s 通\n- **启用 `baidu` / `sogou`** —— 容器内 5.36s / 1.74s 也能通\n- 海外引擎继续 disabled（已经 timeout 没意义）\n\n我直接改 settings.yml 把这三个启用，把海外 general 引擎全 disabled（保留 images/news/videos 等分类的备选）："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0i9f2daa9ujh_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cp /home/halei/searxng-data/settings.yml /home/halei/searxng-data/settings.yml.bak.20260608\necho \"backup ok\"\n# 找出 bing, baidu, sogou 在 settings.yml 里的精确行\ngrep -nE \"name: (bing|baidu|sogou|brave|duckduckgo|google|startpage|wikipedia|presearch|karmasearch)$\" /home/halei/searxng-data/settings.yml"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":7614,"output":331,"cacheRead":61753,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69698,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780923244782,"responseId":"0675ee6d7a2da8250e5261061dac1969"}}
