{"type":"message","id":"0fd3426e","parentId":"6f75ea8d","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:56:40.175Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"嗯，bing 和 sogou 在容器内抓页面超时，但**百度返回了 9 条结果**。等等，number_of_results: 0 但实际有 9 个 results —— 这是 SearXNG 内部计数 bug，不重要。\n\n但 bing/sogou timeout —— 我之前测了容器内 `cn.bing.com` 0.74s 通，怎么 SearXNG 调用就 timeout？看 timeout 设置："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0kqa9vy7hnk7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"docker exec searxng grep -B1 -A 8 \"^  - name: bing$\" /etc/searxng/settings.yml | head -10\necho \"===\"\n# SearXNG 用的 timeout 在哪里设置\ndocker exec searxng grep -n \"timeout\" /etc/searxng/settings.yml | head -10\necho \"===\"\n# 默认 timeout: 3 秒 (SearXNG), 改大点\ndocker exec searxng sh -c 'wget -qO- --timeout=30 \"http://localhost:8080/search?q=test&engines=bing&format=json\" 2>&1' | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\nprint('results:', d.get('number_of_results'))\nprint('unresponsive:', d.get('unresponsive_engines'))\n\"","timeout":90}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":68,"output":306,"cacheRead":76227,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76601,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780923391855,"responseId":"0675ef00432ef6e3ee52f707987d6161"}}
