{"type":"message","id":"3abb28d1","parentId":"9d624c6f","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:56:53.125Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**找到根因**：SearXNG 默认 `request_timeout: 3.0` 秒。容器内 `https://cn.bing.com` 第一次冷连接 8.57s（cold start），后面 0.74s（warm）。bing 引擎的 HTML 解析、提取结果总耗时肯定超 3 秒。\n\n把 `request_timeout` 调大到 10 秒（覆盖在 line 181）："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d2yolzlpjhmi_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"docker exec searxng sh -c '\n# 直接 sed 替换\nsed -i \"s/  request_timeout: 3.0/  request_timeout: 10.0/\" /etc/searxng/settings.yml\ngrep -n \"request_timeout\" /etc/searxng/settings.yml | head -3\n'\ndocker restart searxng\nsleep 8\necho \"--- test bing only ---\"\ndocker exec searxng sh -c 'wget -qO- --timeout=40 \"http://localhost:8080/search?q=test&engines=bing&format=json\" 2>&1' | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\nprint('number_of_results:', d.get('number_of_results'))\nprint('unresponsive:', d.get('unresponsive_engines'))\nprint('engines hit:', {r.get('engine'):None for r in d.get('results',[])})\nprint('first 2 titles:')\nfor r in d.get('results',[])[:3]:\n    print(' -', r.get('title',''))\n\"","timeout":90}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":190,"output":360,"cacheRead":76587,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77137,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780923404264,"responseId":"0675ef0cda21ab71cc271022631fb5f8"}}
