{"type":"message","id":"eeaa4b0a","parentId":"24befb36","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:57:59.333Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**17.22s** —— 容器内抓 bing.com 17 秒，远超 10 秒 timeout。这是**冷连接 + 远距离**导致的固定延迟（甚至可能中间防火墙有 RST 重传）。\n\n把 timeout 调到 30 秒（max_request_timeout 也要调大）："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hr9k23cll0wb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"docker exec searxng sh -c '\nsed -i \"s/  request_timeout: 10.0/  request_timeout: 30.0/\" /etc/searxng/settings.yml\n# 把 max_request_timeout 取消注释并设大\nsed -i \"s/^  # max_request_timeout: 10.0/  max_request_timeout: 30.0/\" /etc/searxng/settings.yml\ngrep -nE \"request_timeout|max_request_timeout\" /etc/searxng/settings.yml | head -5\n'\ndocker restart searxng\nsleep 8\necho \"--- test bing ---\"\nSTART=$(date +%s)\ndocker exec searxng sh -c 'wget -qO- --timeout=50 \"http://localhost:8080/search?q=test&engines=bing&format=json\" 2>&1' > /tmp/searxng_resp.json\nEND=$(date +%s)\necho \"elapsed: $((END-START))s\"\npython3 -c \"\nimport json\nd = json.load(open('/tmp/searxng_resp.json'))\nprint('number_of_results:', d.get('number_of_results'))\nprint('unresponsive:', d.get('unresponsive_engines'))\neng = {}\nfor r in d.get('results', []):\n    eng[r.get('engine','?')] = eng.get(r.get('engine','?'),0)+1\nprint('engines hit:', eng)\nprint('first 3 titles:')\nfor r in d.get('results',[])[:3]:\n    print(' -', r.get('title','')[:80])\n\"","timeout":90}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":52,"output":440,"cacheRead":78122,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78614,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780923467215,"responseId":"0675ef4bfe87dc8a97748c04f98a0f36"}}
