{"type":"message","id":"7d77ebfd","parentId":"f731a520","timestamp":"2026-06-08T13:01:02.926Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**🎉 SearXNG 通过 skill 完整跑通！** 返回 3 条 Bing 结果。\n\n---\n\n现在第二件事：**Hermes 更新**。回到一开始的任务：用户说\"把 hermes 那个项目也更新一下\"。但当时 docker pull 失败（registry 连不通）。我之前查 daemon.json 有 6 个镜像源但大多挂。让我直接**修改 daemon.json 只保留活的源**，然后重启 dockerd，再 pull hermes："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3npe79xq8eps_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /etc/docker/daemon.json\necho\necho \"--- 看活镜像源 ---\"\n# 我已经测过 docker.m.daocloud.io 和 registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com 是活的\n# 让我也试一下 docker.nju.edu.cn / docker.cml.chuheng.com / 168.136.x 这类国内常用\nfor m in docker.m.daocloud.io registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com dockerproxy.cn docker-0.unsee.tech hub-mirror.c.163.com; do\n  printf \"%-45s \" \"$m\"\n  curl -sS -m 4 -o /dev/null -w \"HTTP %{http_code} | %{time_total}s\\n\" \"https://$m/v2/\" 2>&1\ndone","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":354,"output":297,"cacheRead":81456,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82107,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780923653436,"responseId":"0675f0062c500e1917793a5bd75a41d5"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0b0fabbc","parentId":"7d77ebfd","timestamp":"2026-06-08T13:01:06.895Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3npe79xq8eps_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"registry-mirrors\": [\n    \"https://dockerpull.com\",\n    \"https://dhub.kubesre.xyz\",\n    \"https://hub.rat.dev\",\n    \"https://docker.nju.edu.cn\",\n    \"https://registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com\",\n    \"https://registry.docker-cn.com\"\n  ]\n}\n\n--- 看活镜像源 ---\ndocker.m.daocloud.io                          HTTP 401 | 0.208892s\nregistry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com             HTTP 401 | 1.199333s\ndockerproxy.cn                                curl: (6) Could not resolve host: dockerproxy.cn\nHTTP 000 | 0.022967s\ndocker-0.unsee.tech                           HTTP 401 | 1.690869s\nhub-mirror.c.163.com                          curl: (6) Could not resolve host: hub-mirror.c.163.com\nHTTP 000 | 0.025782s\n\n(Command exited with code 6)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":6,"durationMs":3280,"aggregated":"{\n  \"registry-mirrors\": [\n    \"https://dockerpull.com\",\n    \"https://dhub.kubesre.xyz\",\n    \"https://hub.rat.dev\",\n    \"https://docker.nju.edu.cn\",\n    \"https://registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com\",\n    \"https://registry.docker-cn.com\"\n  ]\n}\n\n--- 看活镜像源 ---\ndocker.m.daocloud.io                          HTTP 401 | 0.208892s\nregistry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com             HTTP 401 | 1.199333s\ndockerproxy.cn                                curl: (6) Could not resolve host: dockerproxy.cn\nHTTP 000 | 0.022967s\ndocker-0.unsee.tech                           HTTP 401 | 1.690869s\nhub-mirror.c.163.com                          curl: (6) Could not resolve host: hub-mirror.c.163.com\nHTTP 000 | 0.025782s\n\n(Command exited with code 6)","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780923666894}}
{"type":"message","id":"e3089dd7","parentId":"0b0fabbc","timestamp":"2026-06-08T13:01:17.727Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"3 个活的：`docker.m.daocloud.io` `registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com` `docker-0.unsee.tech`。先**确认 hermes 容器**的具体 image 名 + tag（拉时要用对）："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_t4tndq07sg8o_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"--- hermes image details ---\"\ndocker inspect hermes-agent --format='{{.Config.Image}} | {{.Image}}' 2>&1\necho\necho \"--- 看 hermes 容器里跑的是什么 (entrypoint) ---\"\ndocker inspect hermes-agent --format='{{.Config.Entrypoint}} | {{.Config.Cmd}}' 2>&1\necho\necho \"--- nousresearch/hermes-agent tags on hub (尝试) ---\"\n# 这个可能不通，备用\n# curl -sS -m 6 \"https://hub.docker.com/v2/repositories/nousresearch/hermes-agent/tags/?page_size=5\" 2>&1 | head -c 500\necho \"(skip hub query, registry was timing out before)\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":243,"output":237,"cacheRead":82093,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82573,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780923666923,"responseId":"0675f01815ee763697ea582a4151f6df"}}
{"type":"message","id":"506a7852","parentId":"e3089dd7","timestamp":"2026-06-08T13:01:18.608Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_t4tndq07sg8o_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"--- hermes image details ---\nnousresearch/hermes-agent | sha256:5a52be6728aa02d2050bea70d73c3d740ded9c153ce5a963f685d0b64ece9614\n\n--- 看 hermes 容器里跑的是什么 (entrypoint) ---\n[/init /opt/hermes/docker/main-wrapper.sh] | [gateway run]\n\n--- nousresearch/hermes-agent tags on hub (尝试) ---\n(skip hub query, registry was timing out before)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":140,"aggregated":"--- hermes image details ---\nnousresearch/hermes-agent | sha256:5a52be6728aa02d2050bea70d73c3d740ded9c153ce5a963f685d0b64ece9614\n\n--- 看 hermes 容器里跑的是什么 (entrypoint) ---\n[/init /opt/hermes/docker/main-wrapper.sh] | [gateway run]\n\n--- nousresearch/hermes-agent tags on hub (尝试) ---\n(skip hub query, registry was timing out before)","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780923678605}}
{"type":"message","id":"a035e073","parentId":"506a7852","timestamp":"2026-06-08T13:01:24.383Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Hermes 镜像：`nousresearch/hermes-agent`（默认 latest tag）。entrypoint 是 `/opt/hermes/docker/main-wrapper.sh gateway run`。\n\n现在改 daemon.json，把死的源去掉，加活的源，然后重启 dockerd："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5o01qo3px4s7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 备份\nsudo -n cp /etc/docker/daemon.json /etc/docker/daemon.json.bak 2>&1 || cp /etc/docker/daemon.json /tmp/daemon.json.bak\nls -la /tmp/daemon.json.bak 2>&1\necho\n# 写新的 daemon.json (用 sudo -n 不行，文件是 root:root 644)\nls -la /etc/docker/daemon.json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":136,"output":164,"cacheRead":82559,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82859,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780923678641,"responseId":"0675f01f8f17541127a488b703a65c10"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8673ad92","parentId":"a035e073","timestamp":"2026-06-08T13:01:25.244Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5o01qo3px4s7_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"sudo: 需要密码\n-rw-r--r-- 1 halei halei 240  6月  8 21:01 /tmp/daemon.json.bak\n\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 240  4月  5 22:47 /etc/docker/daemon.json"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":330,"aggregated":"sudo: 需要密码\n-rw-r--r-- 1 halei halei 240  6月  8 21:01 /tmp/daemon.json.bak\n\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 240  4月  5 22:47 /etc/docker/daemon.json","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780923685238}}
{"type":"message","id":"e1fee60f","parentId":"8673ad92","timestamp":"2026-06-08T13:01:35.710Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"文件 root:root，我用 `sudo` 不通，让我用 `pkexec` 或别的方式，或者用 python 写（不行，root 才有权限），或者... 我没有 root 密码。\n\n但等等：dockerd 是 root 跑的，**用户加入 docker 组后 `docker` 命令本身会通过 docker socket 跟 dockerd 通信**，但写 /etc/docker/daemon.json 需要 root。\n\n**有两个办法**：\n1. 让用户帮写 daemon.json（4 行 JSON）\n2. 直接告诉 dockerd reload mirror 列表 —— 但 daemon.json 改了必须 SIGHUP 或重启 dockerd 才能生效\n3. 用 **daemon-less 方式**：通过环境变量 `DOCKER_REGISTRY_MIRROR` 或 dockerd 启动参数（已太晚）\n\n我得让用户帮忙。或者... 检查下 docker socket 权限："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g8aowkq02bny_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /var/run/docker.sock\necho \"---\"\ngroups halei\nid halei\necho \"---\"\n# 我是 docker 组吗？能用 docker 命令说明是的\ndocker version 2>&1 | head -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":100,"output":249,"cacheRead":82845,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83194,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780923685279,"responseId":"0675f0268615b3f3730f2f56b5071a59"}}
{"type":"message","id":"30a3fc91","parentId":"e1fee60f","timestamp":"2026-06-08T13:01:36.586Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_g8aowkq02bny_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"srw-rw---- 1 root docker 0  5月 27 20:29 /var/run/docker.sock\n---\nhalei : halei adm cdrom sudo dip plugdev lpadmin lxd sambashare docker\nuid=1000(halei) gid=1000(halei) 组=1000(halei),4(adm),24(cdrom),27(sudo),30(dip),46(plugdev),122(lpadmin),135(lxd),136(sambashare),137(docker)\n---\nClient:\n Version:           29.1.3\n API version:       1.52\n Go version:        go1.24.4\n Git commit:        29.1.3-0ubuntu3~22.04.2"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":135,"aggregated":"srw-rw---- 1 root docker 0  5月 27 20:29 /var/run/docker.sock\n---\nhalei : halei adm cdrom sudo dip plugdev lpadmin lxd sambashare docker\nuid=1000(halei) gid=1000(halei) 组=1000(halei),4(adm),24(cdrom),27(sudo),30(dip),46(plugdev),122(lpadmin),135(lxd),136(sambashare),137(docker)\n---\nClient:\n Version:           29.1.3\n API version:       1.52\n Go version:        go1.24.4\n Git commit:        29.1.3-0ubuntu3~22.04.2","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780923696580}}
{"type":"message","id":"3b00f350","parentId":"30a3fc91","timestamp":"2026-06-08T13:01:50.575Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我是 `sudo` 组。**`sudo` 组意味着能用密码 sudo**，但**无密码 sudo 不行**（`sudo -n` 报需要密码）。但我**有 sudo 权限**，只是没有自动给密码。这个情况下我应该**让用户确认**改 daemon.json + 重启 dockerd 是高风险操作（重启会停掉所有容器包括 searxng 本身），必须确认。\n\n而且从用户角度：**改 dockerd 配置 = 影响全局**，agent-orchestrator 边界说\"agent 设置交由 agent-orchestrator\"，这里 dockerd 是基础设施但也是 agent-orchestrator 管辖范围。\n\n**但用户明确要求\"你通过docker检查一下这个项目有更新吗, 把hermes那个项目也更新一下\"**——这是显式请求更新，我应该执行。但 daemon.json 修改 + dockerd 重启是副作用大、需要用户确认的步骤。\n\n策略：\n1. 先告知用户当前状况（searxng 修好了，hermes 需要改 mirror 才能 pull）\n2. 让用户决定怎么处理 daemon.json（自己改 / 我用 sudo 改 / 用其他方法）\n3. 或：先尝试不用改 daemon.json，而是用 `docker pull <mirror>/nousresearch/hermes-agent` 这种**手动指定 mirror** 的方式直接拉，再 retag\n\n实际上 docker 不支持直接通过 URL 指定 mirror 在 pull 时。但我们可以通过 daemon.json 的 `registry-mirrors` 试一下：dockerd 启动时如果 mirror 列表里的都失败，会 fallback 到主 registry。问题是主 registry 也不通。\n\n**更优解**：让我看看**当前 daemon.json 里的 mirror** dockerd 是否真的在用。可能 dockerd 启动时 mirror 列表是空的（`dockerpull.com` 之类都死），导致实际不 mirror："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p03yz3sv2gl6_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"docker info 2>&1 | grep -A 20 \"Registry Mirrors\" | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":199,"output":418,"cacheRead":83180,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83797,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780923696619,"responseId":"0675f0312da4fc10cfe8944d006672cc"}}
{"type":"message","id":"24fd264e","parentId":"3b00f350","timestamp":"2026-06-08T13:01:51.514Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_p03yz3sv2gl6_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Registry Mirrors:\n  https://dockerpull.com/\n  https://dhub.kubesre.xyz/\n  https://hub.rat.dev/\n  https://docker.nju.edu.cn/\n  https://registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/\n  https://registry.docker-cn.com/\n Live Restore Enabled: false\n Firewall Backend: iptables"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":246,"aggregated":"Registry Mirrors:\n  https://dockerpull.com/\n  https://dhub.kubesre.xyz/\n  https://hub.rat.dev/\n  https://docker.nju.edu.cn/\n  https://registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/\n  https://registry.docker-cn.com/\n Live Restore Enabled: false\n Firewall Backend: iptables","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780923711513}}
{"type":"message","id":"1d25ae6e","parentId":"24fd264e","timestamp":"2026-06-08T13:02:04.971Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"6 个 mirror 都列着但都不工作（之前 pull 走的还是 registry-1.docker.io）。这说明 dockerd 试了 mirror 都失败然后去主 registry 主 registry 也失败。\n\n**关键洞察**：我的 SearXNG 修好是因为**容器内本身能通 cn.bing.com / baidu / sogou**。但容器内部用的是 host network 的某种配置（或者直接走 docker0 bridge 出公网）。dockerd 本身（host 上的进程）拉镜像时——它走的是 host 自己的网络栈。\n\n**对啊！** 之前 curl `https://cn.bing.com` 从 host 测，timeout 4 秒。host 出的 443 被防火墙挡。但 SearXNG 容器内能通 443 8 秒连 bing。所以：**容器内的网络和 host 的网络走了不同出口**。\n\n可能的原因：\n- Docker 默认 bridge 网桥 + iptables MASQUERADE，容器走的是**另一个网络出口**（也许有特殊路由）\n- 或者 host 上有别的内网网卡\n\n看一下："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8dcfk9jm1txz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"--- host network ---\"\nip route 2>&1\necho\nip -4 addr 2>&1\necho\necho \"--- host curl cn.bing.com (对比) ---\"\ncurl -sS -m 6 -o /dev/null -w \"HTTP %{http_code} | %{time_total}s\\n\" \"https://cn.bing.com\" 2>&1\necho\necho \"--- host curl baidu ---\"\ncurl -sS -m 6 -o /dev/null -w \"HTTP %{http_code} | %{time_total}s\\n\" \"https://www.baidu.com\" 2>&1\necho\necho \"--- container view of network ---\"\ndocker exec searxng ip route 2>&1\necho \"---\"\ndocker exec searxng ip -4 addr 2>&1 | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":103,"output":423,"cacheRead":83783,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84309,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780923711545,"responseId":"0675f03f6d0e6bcca2da098ce79a73de"}}
