{"type":"message","id":"09f01d4d","parentId":"a52c1969","timestamp":"2026-06-08T13:02:21.173Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**重要修正**：\n- 刚才 host `curl cn.bing.com` **HTTP 200 | 3.4s** —— **能通！**\n- host `curl baidu` **0.17s** —— 超快\n- **之前我以为 host 的 443 都被挡是错的！** 是因为 dockerd 拉镜像时 `registry-1.docker.io` 解析到的是 Cloudflare 的 IPv6，host 没有 IPv6 出口，导致连不上。\n\n所以**问题不在防火墙**，是 dockerd 解析 `registry-1.docker.io` 拿到的是 IPv6，而 host 没 IPv6 出口。让我用 IPv4 测一下："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_166rn4l8ncwv_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"--- IPv4 vs IPv6 for registry-1.docker.io ---\"\n# 强制 IPv4\ncurl -sS -m 6 -4 -o /dev/null -w \"IPv4: HTTP %{http_code} | %{time_total}s\\n\" \"https://registry-1.docker.io/v2/\" 2>&1\ncurl -sS -m 6 -6 -o /dev/null -w \"IPv6: HTTP %{http_code} | %{time_total}s\\n\" \"https://registry-1.docker.io/v2/\" 2>&1\necho\necho \"--- IPv4 for production cloudflare ---\"\ncurl -sS -m 6 -4 -o /dev/null -w \"HTTP %{http_code} | %{time_total}s\\n\" \"https://1.1.1.1\" 2>&1\necho\necho \"--- daemon uses 8.8.8.8 (no IPv6) for upstream DNS ---\"\ncat /etc/resolv.conf 2>&1 | head -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":16357,"output":382,"cacheRead":69353,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86092,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780923729295,"responseId":"0675f0512bdb5b67c9aaac85187ebae0"}}
