{"type":"message","id":"d16f7b1b","parentId":"4c6ae1ae","timestamp":"2026-06-08T13:02:36.785Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pwthpje7i54y_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"--- IPv4 vs IPv6 for registry-1.docker.io ---\ncurl: (28) Failed to connect to registry-1.docker.io port 443 after 3026 ms: 连接超时\nIPv4: HTTP 000 | 3.026666s\ncurl: (28) Failed to connect to registry-1.docker.io port 443 after 3002 ms: 连接超时\nIPv6: HTTP 000 | 3.002629s\n\n--- IPv4 for production cloudflare ---\ncurl: (28) Connection timed out after 6001 milliseconds\nHTTP 000 | 6.001650s\n\n--- daemon uses 8.8.8.8 (no IPv6) for upstream DNS ---\n# This is /run/systemd/resolve/stub-resolv.conf managed by man:systemd-resolved(8).\n# Do not edit.\n#\n# This file might be symlinked as /etc/resolv.conf. If you're looking at\n# /etc/resolv.conf and seeing this text, you have followed the symlink.\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"mild-claw","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"--- IPv4 vs IPv6 for registry-1.docker.io ---\ncurl: (28) Failed to connect to registry-1.docker.io port 443 after 3026 ms: 连接超时\nIPv4: HTTP 000 | 3.026666s\ncurl: (28) Failed to connect to registry-1.docker.io port 443 after 3002 ms: 连接超时\nIPv6: HTTP 000 | 3.002629s\n\n--- IPv4 for production cloudflare ---\ncurl: (28) Connection timed out after 6001 milliseconds\nHTTP 000 | 6.001650s\n\n--- daemon uses 8.8.8.8 (no IPv6) for upstream DNS ---\n# This is /run/systemd/resolve/stub-resolv.conf managed by man:systemd-resolved(8).\n# Do not edit.\n#\n# This file might be symlinked as /etc/resolv.conf. If you're looking at\n# /etc/resolv.conf and seeing this text, you have followed the symlink.\n","name":"echo #"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780923756784}}
{"type":"message","id":"05b7f0c4","parentId":"d16f7b1b","timestamp":"2026-06-08T13:02:45.232Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"啊有意思：\n- `registry-1.docker.io` IPv4 也不通\n- `1.1.1.1` 也不通\n- 但 `cn.bing.com` `baidu.com` 通\n\n`registry-1.docker.io` 的 A 记录和 `1.1.1.1` 应该都是 Cloudflare 节点。让我看下到底 IP 是什么："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_aashddu1fv6g_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"--- IP addresses for registry-1.docker.io (force IPv4) ---\"\ngetent ahosts registry-1.docker.io 2>&1\necho\necho \"--- ip route for these IPs ---\"\n# 列出所有 IP 路由\nfor ip in $(getent ahosts registry-1.docker.io | awk '{print $1}' | sort -u); do\n  printf \"%-40s \" \"$ip\"\n  ip route get \"$ip\" 2>&1\ndone\necho\necho \"--- IP for cn.bing.com ---\"\ngetent ahosts cn.bing.com 2>&1\necho\necho \"--- IP for hub.docker.com ---\"\ngetent ahosts hub.docker.com 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":251,"output":257,"cacheRead":86182,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86690,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780923756815,"responseId":"0675f06d7033a82f3a4109e760ad7580"}}
{"type":"message","id":"76cb4724","parentId":"05b7f0c4","timestamp":"2026-06-08T13:02:46.105Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_aashddu1fv6g_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"--- IP addresses for registry-1.docker.io (force IPv4) ---\n185.45.7.165    STREAM registry-1.docker.io\n185.45.7.165    DGRAM  \n185.45.7.165    RAW    \n2001::6817:7cbd STREAM \n2001::6817:7cbd DGRAM  \n2001::6817:7cbd RAW    \n\n--- ip route for these IPs ---\n185.45.7.165                             185.45.7.165 via 192.168.31.1 dev wlp2s0 src 192.168.31.146 uid 1000 \n    cache \n2001::6817:7cbd                          2001::6817:7cbd from :: via fe80::5288:11ff:feaf:4a79 dev wlp2s0 proto ra src 2409:8a00:6c85:9394:a695:ca67:767b:7ac7 metric 600 pref medium\n\n--- IP for cn.bing.com ---\n202.89.233.101  STREAM china.bing123.com\n202.89.233.101  DGRAM  \n202.89.233.101  RAW    \n202.89.233.100  STREAM \n202.89.233.100  DGRAM  \n202.89.233.100  RAW    \n\n--- IP for hub.docker.com ---\n2a03:2880:f107:83:face:b00c:0:25de STREAM hub.docker.com\n2a03:2880:f107:83:face:b00c:0:25de DGRAM  \n2a03:2880:f107:83:face:b00c:0:25de RAW    \n199.59.149.204  STREAM \n199.59.149.204  DGRAM  \n199.59.149.204  RAW"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":215,"aggregated":"--- IP addresses for registry-1.docker.io (force IPv4) ---\n185.45.7.165    STREAM registry-1.docker.io\n185.45.7.165    DGRAM  \n185.45.7.165    RAW    \n2001::6817:7cbd STREAM \n2001::6817:7cbd DGRAM  \n2001::6817:7cbd RAW    \n\n--- ip route for these IPs ---\n185.45.7.165                             185.45.7.165 via 192.168.31.1 dev wlp2s0 src 192.168.31.146 uid 1000 \n    cache \n2001::6817:7cbd                          2001::6817:7cbd from :: via fe80::5288:11ff:feaf:4a79 dev wlp2s0 proto ra src 2409:8a00:6c85:9394:a695:ca67:767b:7ac7 metric 600 pref medium\n\n--- IP for cn.bing.com ---\n202.89.233.101  STREAM china.bing123.com\n202.89.233.101  DGRAM  \n202.89.233.101