{"type":"message","id":"3289779e","parentId":"76cb4724","timestamp":"2026-06-08T13:02:54.987Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**关键发现**：\n- `registry-1.docker.io` 解析到 `185.45.7.165`（IPv4 德国机房）和 `2001::6817:7cbd`（IPv6）\n- `cn.bing.com` 解析到 `202.89.233.100-101`（**国内 IP**）\n- `hub.docker.com` 解析到 `199.59.149.204`（**美国**）\n\n所以 host 能访问的是**国内 IP 段**，**海外 IP 段被防火墙/路由挡了**。`registry-1.docker.io` 解析到德国 IP，host 出不去。\n\n但 dockerd 配的 mirror 大多数都死了。**3 个活的镜像源（`docker.m.daocloud.io` `registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com` `docker-0.unsee.tech`）应该在国内**，让我测一下它们域名解析的 IP："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pabfunwuxu4j_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"for m in docker.m.daocloud.io registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com docker-0.unsee.tech; do\n  echo \"=== $m ===\"\n  getent ahosts \"$m\" 2>&1\ndone"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":438,"output":276,"cacheRead":86676,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87390,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780923766136,"responseId":"0675f076614661d409438b25b4f2a66e"}}
